	<strong>About Us</strong></p>
<p>
	<span data-scayt_word="Intermedia.NET" data-scaytid="1">Intermedia.NET</span> is the leading provider of cloud based email to the <span data-scayt_word="SMB" data-scaytid="2">SMB</span> marketplace. We are looking for a self-motivated, enthusiastic, organized, and results-oriented person with a good phone personality and some knowledge of IT and the internet. This is a <span data-scayt_word="launchpad" data-scaytid="3">launchpad</span> position for a sales career, with a company that will help you develop your sales skills and provide you with an opportunity for advancement. This position is base out of our NY, NY office.</p>
<p>
	<strong>The major responsibilities of this position include:</strong></p>
<ul>
	<li>
		Calling out to existing accounts with identified <span data-scayt_word="upsell" data-scaytid="4">upsell</span> &amp; cross selling opportunities</li>
	<li>
		Sell our hosted Exchange plans to new customers from inbound leads and phone calls</li>
	<li>
		Assisting customers with request for platform migrations, and plan changes</li>
</ul>
<p>
	<strong>Requirements: </strong></p>
<ul>
	<li>
		The ability to persuade and motivate is the key requirement of this inside sales position.</li>
	<li>
		Must be an excellent telephone communicator with a pleasant and firm phone voice.</li>
	<li>
		Ability to provide a persuasive verbal presentation.</li>
	<li>
		Ability to articulate well via written media, including letters, emails and Instant Messages.</li>
	<li>
		Able to demonstrate ability to communicate with small and medium sized business customers of varying technical and business sophistication.</li>
	<li>
		Above average problem solving skills.</li>
	<li>
		Strong analytic and MS Excel skills a plus.</li>
</ul>
<p>
	<strong>Not required - but a plus:</strong></p>
<ul>
	<li>
		Knowledge of Microsoft Outlook/Exchange&nbsp;</li>
	<li>
		Mobility solutions (BlackBerry other <span data-scayt_word="Smartphones" data-scaytid="5">Smartphones</span>, etc.)</li>
	<li>
		Web hosting and other web-based services offered by.</li>
	<li>
		Some technical background a plus.</li>
</ul>
